# AIHubMix

Use `aihubmix/<model>` with VoltAgent's model router.

## Quick start

```ts
import { Agent } from "@voltagent/core";

const agent = new Agent({
  name: "aihubmix-agent",
  instructions: "You are a helpful assistant",
  model: "aihubmix/Kimi-K2-0905",
});
```

## Environment variables

- `AIHUBMIX_API_KEY`

## Provider package

`@aihubmix/ai-sdk-provider`

## Default base URL

Not listed.

You can override the base URL by setting `AIHUBMIX_BASE_URL`.
